description.en: Rooster Teeth is a pioneering media and entertainment company responsible for some of the biggest online series in history, such as the award-winning and longest-running web series, Red vs. Blue
description.ga_IE: Is cuideachta mheáin chumarsáide agus siamsaíochta é fiacla Rooster atá freagrach as cuid de na sraitheanna ar líne is mó i stair, mar shampla an tsraith gréasáin a bhuaigh duaiseanna agus is faide an-rith, dearg vs gorm
